Andrew! Andrew!

04:09.450 --> 04:10.649
I'm coming!

04:10.651 --> 04:12.051
Jesus, Baz.

04:12.053 --> 04:13.652
This ain't no damn
Sunday stroll.

04:13.654 --> 04:15.654
Let's go!
Get the back!

04:15.656 --> 04:25.398
♪♪

04:25.400 --> 04:34.940
