04:34.942 --> 04:39.612
♪♪

04:39.614 --> 04:41.346
Yeah, that's good.

04:41.348 --> 04:43.548
Julia.

04:43.550 --> 04:46.752
[ Music playing
over headphones ]

04:46.754 --> 04:48.888
Mr. Martin.

04:48.890 --> 04:50.956
What are you doing here?
It's Saturday.

04:50.958 --> 04:53.225
SAT prep.

04:53.227 --> 04:55.761
Right.
I-I forgot.

04:55.763 --> 04:57.096
Why are you here?

04:57.098 --> 04:59.632
Um, I-I left "A Separate Peace"
in my locker.

04:59.634 --> 05:02.902
Yeah, well, paper's due Monday.
Cutting it close, huh?

05:02.904 --> 05:05.304
I guess so.

05:05.306 --> 05:08.307
♪♪

05:08.309 --> 05:10.243
