your twin brother?

05:10.245 --> 05:12.445
No.

05:12.447 --> 05:15.848
Yeah, that was Andrew
by the library.

05:15.850 --> 05:18.117
No, Andrew --
I-I'm pretty sure he's at home,

05:18.119 --> 05:20.319
so i-it can't be --
-What's going on here, Julia?

05:20.321 --> 05:24.723
♪♪

05:24.725 --> 05:28.527
[ Sighs ] Goddamn it.

05:28.529 --> 05:29.662
Come with me.

05:29.664 --> 05:30.863
-No, no --
-Come with me.

05:30.865 --> 05:32.665
Let go!

05:32.667 --> 05:35.000
Julia!
A teacher stopped her.

05:35.002 --> 05:37.536
-Shit.
-I gotta go get her.

05:37.538 --> 05:40.405
-No, Andrew!
-I'll be back, Baz.

05:40.407 --> 05:42.808
