-Yeah, I know! He hit a teacher!

06:43.938 --> 06:46.339
♪ Gotta find a way,
find a way, when I'm there ♪

06:46.341 --> 06:48.741
There he is.

06:48.743 --> 06:53.078
♪ Gotta find a way,
a better way, I'd better wait ♪

06:53.080 --> 06:54.613
-Andrew, run!
-Hurry up, Andrew!

06:54.615 --> 06:59.084
♪ Gotta find a way,
find a way, when I'm there ♪

06:59.086 --> 07:01.887
Oh, my God. I -- No, I have to!
I have to get him!

07:01.889 --> 07:03.622
Julia!

07:03.624 --> 07:05.558
Andrew, stop!

07:05.560 --> 07:08.160
Stop! Stop!

07:08.162 --> 07:11.230
Get off of him!
Let go of him!

07:11.232 --> 07:12.765
